<div class="com-share" data-id="1223" data-title="《LGBT中国报告二：粉红市场》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/1223/medium/1223.jpg?1436639489" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/1223" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
